<i>Posted by Toastedzergling on Sep 16, 2002 02:29 PM:</i>

<p><b> </b></p>

<p>In one of my deity games I had fun watching Romans and Greeks warring at my territory for hundreds of years, I had fought Romans with Greece before but when Caesar declared a new war againt Alexander I decided to pass. I paid ROPs for both of them to speed things up, and sold iron and my only source of salper to Greece to help them out. I used my troops to block the way so that Roman could not combine their forces for town siege<img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt=""> Despite my effort, Greece was losing the war and eventually forced to sign peace treaty.<br />
<br />
The next turn Roman declared war with me, and captured a couple of my cities, including the one I am working on a forbidden palace.  <img src="images/smilies/mad.gif" border="0" alt=""> <br />
<br />
Eventually I won the war against Romans, but the damage was done.</p>
