The AIs do not want to sign the ROP with you.  They want to able to go every where and walk all over your empire as they please; however, they do not wish to see you setting foot on their empire.   So basically, no ROP deal, but don't border asking them to leave either.<img src="images/smilies/biggrin.gif" border="0" alt=""></p>


